item.title: Single Room
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Enjoy your stay while on a business trip or traveling leisure, with all the amenities and comforts which our hotel's single rooms have. This always includes a TV, shower and a free Internet access....

item.title: Double Room
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: This is the ultimate double room, enhanced with 2 king sized beds, a flat TV, and a spacious area, which will be more than enough for a company of two... Additionally, the room features an option to have either a double-sized bed or two single beds.

item.title: Family Room
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Ideal for families of 3 or even 4 people, this room is spacious and comfortable enough for both you and your children to have fun, relax or simply sleep over while traveling... It will make your stay even more pleasant!

item.title: Suite
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Enjoy our classic suites with all the elegancy and comfort that its interior has... It features such essentials as a flat-screen 45" TV, WiFi and 2 bathrooms with a living room and 2 bedrooms, big and chic enough to be counted as real suite bedrooms!
item.excerpt:encoded:

  • Breakfast included
  • Price does not include VAT & services fee

item.title: Single room with balcony
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: This enhanced single room has an advantage of having a great view and a bay window... Enjoy your stay while on a business trip or traveling leisure, with all the amenities and comfort that we have to offer!

item.title: Weddings & Honeymooons
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Free for all visitors except Single Rooms
Being such a luxurious hotel located in such an exotic part of the world as Africa and in a country as colorful as Namibia, we get tons of wedding & honeymoon requests throughout the year. While perfectly suited for that, we maintain a waiting list.

item.title: Dining & Drinking
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Prices depend on the menu items you order
Considering just how diverse & different the whole food culture & dishes of cuisine are in Africa, you'd sure love to try best local food & beverages! The menu we have here includes both the best food, alcoholic and NA drinks that Namibia has to offer.

item.title: SPA & Wellness
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Prices start at $180.00
Due to the fact just how luxurious and exotic it is to travel to Namibia and stay at our hotel, we've taken care of providing you with additional services. SPA, massages and other wellness treatments make sure that you get as relaxed as possible...

item.title: Local Festivals
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Prices start at $380.00/hour
What is the very first thing, an association that comes to your mind as soon as you hear the word Namibia? Surely it's the Oohakawinoo festival that the locals hold! This just as well as hundreds other local festivities will be within a grasp away when you're staying at out place!

Faq

Working in the hospitality industry for a long time, we've got used to a lot of similar questions that our visitors tend to ask us. Here we've compiled all of those into one comprehensive list, for everyone's convenience!
[/tm_pb_text][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][tm_pb_row admin_label="Row" make_fullwidth="off" use_custom_width="off" use_grid_padding="on" width_unit="on" custom_padding="|15%|90px|15%" custom_padding_tablet="|0px|90px|0px" custom_padding_last_edited="on|desktop" padding_mobile="off" allow_player_pause="off" parallax="off" parallax_method="off" make_equal="off" parallax_1="off" parallax_method_1="off" column_padding_mobile="on" custom_padding_phone="|0px|30px|0px"][tm_pb_column type="4_4"][tm_pb_toggle admin_label="Toggle" title="Can our organization book your hotel for our annual conference?" open="off" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid"]

While that is possible, it may prove to be difficult to book all of our hotel rooms at the same time.

We're usually quite overbooked, which on par with a considerably small number of rooms available in the hotel accounts to a waiting booking list.

If your party is planning to attend soon, please book us as beforehand as possible!

[/tm_pb_toggle][tm_pb_toggle admin_label="Toggle" title="Do you offer concierge services?" open="on" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid"] Yes. Those are available for our family room and suites guests. [/tm_pb_toggle][tm_pb_toggle admin_label="Toggle" title="Can I bring my pet into the hotel?" open="off" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid"]

As a rule, we allow only specific types of pets to be admitted into the hotel rooms.

Exceptions for suite guests apply.

[/tm_pb_toggle][tm_pb_toggle admin_label="Toggle" title="Do you have a conference hall for hosting business meetings?" open="off" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid"]

Absolutely!
In fact, we have two conference rooms and we cater your business meetings with both food menu items and beverages!

[/tm_pb_toggle][tm_pb_toggle admin_label="Toggle" title="Why is your pricing cheaper, as opposed to other Indianapolis hotels of the same class?" open="off" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid"] We guess that is the matter of optimizing everything we do, in order to keep both the quality standards and rules and the pricing intact. When you need your company to have a new website or if you venture on updating your old webpage with a new look and functionality, the choices are versatile… Assuming that you will go the easy way and choose a theme for your Wordpress website, the overall number of characteristics that you will need to keep in mind narrows down significantly. But how do you stay focused on what kind of a template you need and what do you want to get from that template? We recommend focusing on 4 most essential characteristics, each vital for your company’s to have an efficient and long-standing online presence!
Design & Functionality are the main features to focus on when you are about to choose the permanent look for your website!
